This paper discusses the use of computational methods in analyzing and synthesizing registers in language research. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the arXiv category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning and artificial intelligence in this field, which makes it relevant to the categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of data analysis and mapping, which makes it relevant to the categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
